  "body": "\r\n***Type***: Bug\r\n\r\n***Summary***: Right to left text messages aligned to the right in the message bubble and it overlaps message timestamp. We need to take into account, and when the \"align text to the right\" event is triggered in message bubble - consider a margin of the message timestamp. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nRight to left text messages does not overlap timestamp in the message bubble\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nRight to left text messages aligned to the right in the message bubble and does not overlap message timestamp.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"291\" alt=\"screen shot 2018-05-16 at 16 59 25\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/40121596-966200da-592a-11e8-9fbd-d656ac539732.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Navigate to any type of chat\r\n- Type arabic text and send (e.g. `أنت محظوظ اليوم!`)\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: Develop/Release 0.9.18\r\n* Operating System: Android and iOS\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\nTF session: https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8304711/sessions/55/?accessToken=gbz/I01Osj4ZslRk28TSQFBW4x8\n\n<blockquote><div><strong><a href=\"https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8304711/sessions/55/?accessToken=gbz/I01Osj4ZslRk28TSQFBW4x8\">TestFairy: Status 0.9.16-169-gaa108cda+ (2596) @55</a></strong></div></blockquote>",
